{
  "id" : 811,
  "songNumber" : 199,
  "title" : "DOWN FROM HIS GLORY",
  "language" : "english",
  "originalKey" : "D",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Down from His glory, ever living story,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "My God and Saviour came, and Jesus was His Name.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 29
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 35
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 43
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Born in a manger, to His own a stranger,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "A Man of sorrow, tears and agony.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 17
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 27
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "CHORUS",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "O how I love Him! How I adore Him!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "My breath, my sunshine, my all in all!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 27
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The great Creator became my Saviour,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 28
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And all God's fullness dwelleth in Him,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 28
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "What condescension, bringing us redemption;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "That in the dead of night, not one faint hope in sight;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 31
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 49
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "God, gracious, tender, laid aside His splendour,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Stooping to woo, to win, to save my soul.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 28
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 36
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Without reluctance, flesh and blood His substance,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He took the form of man, revealed the hidden plan.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 27
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 45
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "O glorious mystery, Sacrifice of Calvary,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And now I know Thou wert the great \"I AM.\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 29
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    } ]
  } ]
}